⚠️ Critical:Publicly Accessible must be set to YES — otherwise you cannot connect from your local computer or SQL Electron. This is the most common mistake.

Step 8 — Additional Configuration:

Expand "Additional Configuration" section
Configure:
Table


Setting	Value
